&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div id="orged8316d" class="figure"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="hold-the-pie/why_pie.png" alt="why_pie.png" /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul class="org-ul"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ok, first of all, it's &lt;a href="https://blogs.oracle.com/experience/entry/countdown_of_top_10_reasons_to_never_ever_use_a_pie_chart"&gt;a&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pie_chart"&gt;pie&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/pie-charts-are-the-worst-2013-6"&gt;chart&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
